= TTF_SetFontSize =

Set font size dynamically.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int TTF_SetFontSize(TTF_Font *font, int ptsize);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''font'''
|[[TTF_Font]] handle
|-
|'''ptsize'''
|point size
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns 0 if successful, -1 on error

== Remarks ==

This clears already generated glyphs, if any, from the cache.

